# start Validation Reply Form
_vrf_THETM01_6_meo_naphthalene_butyl_pbi4 
;
PROBLEM: The value of sine(theta_max)/wavelength is less than 0.550
RESPONSE: Despite long exposure time, no diffraction was observed past 0.98A and we are confident in the reported solution and refinement
;
_vrf_PLAT342_6_meo_naphthalene_butyl_pbi4 
;
PROBLEM: Low Bond Precision on  C-C Bonds ...............    0.03214 Ang.
